title: Analyzing NHL Data from 2007-2008 to 2018-2019
text:
library(nhldata)
library(dplyr)
library(lubridate)
library(tidyr)
library(ggplot2)


teams %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = season, y = gf, color = team)) + 
  geom_line()

`geom_line()`: Each group consists of only one observation.
ℹ Do you need to adjust the group aesthetic?
